{"tid":1919823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】科大新智能殺菌塗層 MAP-1   殺菌期最長90天 + 可製口罩、過濾網、衣服","createTime":"2020-03-11T04:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T05:16:34.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8b5325be70f7012de1fac3ba5ebd990bea6e2b0e","tid":1919823,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T04:49:41.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯新殺菌塗層由科大化學及生物工程學系兼環境及可持續發展部楊經倫教授領導的開發團隊研發。在九龍醫院、靈實胡平頤養院兩項臨床試驗中，被證實對殺死抗藥性微生物細菌十分有效。楊經倫教授指：「在為期分別 7 個月與 6 個月的臨床試驗中，隔簾與床單的細菌總量分別下降了逾 99% 以及 95.8%，結果令人鼓舞。」<br />\n <br />\n塗層殺菌期最長可達 90 日，可在金屬、混凝土、木材、玻璃、塑料、織物、皮革、纖維等不同物料的表面，提供長效消毒與抗菌保護⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/03/11/germagicust/life-tech/health/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F03%2F11%2Fgermagicust%2Flife-tech%2Fhealth%2F&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=b015f18f\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/03/11/germagicust/life-tech/health/</a>"},{"pid":"4974d439edf67104276d736dfa85ee9f1f6ba39f","tid":1919823,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T04:51:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"526bbf5b23a6bf233bcf45e489b27eed5a82c1ae","tid":1919823,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T04:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d08b99de0e90372fb6109ed238a895901583f85","tid":1919823,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T04:54:19.000Z","msg":"噴入肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cd8cb1fcf03d0028e448e9bf7f25726a43d355","tid":1919823,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d08b99de0e90372fb6109ed238a895901583f85","tid":1919823,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T04:54:19.000Z","msg":"噴入肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202